mixin fixedInvestment
	section.section.section--gray-dark.fixed-investment.mobile-dropdown__content(data-panel="fixed-investment" data-target="fixed-investment")
		div.container
			div.row
				div.col-lg-10.col-lg-offset-1
					div.row.fixed-investment__intro
						div.col-md-6
							h2.comprehensive-intro__heading 債券投資信託
							h3.comprehensive-intro__subheading 債券は本来ディフェンシブ（防御的）な投資商品です。
							div.row
								div.col-sm-6.fixed-investment__workflow
									div.fixed-investment__content
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-start 確定した満期日
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-process
											div.fixed-investment__workflow-cell 確定した満期日
												br
												| に額面を払い戻し　
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-end 満期日では元本保証
								div.col-sm-6.fixed-investment__workflow
									div.fixed-investment__content
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-start 確定した支払日
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-process
											div.fixed-investment__workflow-cell 満期日では元本保証
												br
												| 定期的にクーポンの受け取り
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-end 満期日までの確定した収入
						div.col-md-6
							div.fixed-investment__right-panel
								h2.comprehensive-intro__heading 当社は、債権ポートフォリオについては
								h3.comprehensive-intro__subheading 諸要素を勘案した投資を行います
